org.xflatdb.xflat.query

Class Interval<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xflatdb.xflat.query.Interval<T>

  • public class Interval<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents one interval within an interval set. The interval is represented by two values, the begin and the end, which can be inclusive or exclusive.
